@{b}The Better versions@{ub}
===================

Well here we have the FULL Version. 

All bugs have been fixed and a couple of extra bits added.

1) There is a help tool that either pages me or if I am not online,
   gives you the opportunity to mail me directly.

2) The one program at a time bug has been fixed aswell as the SHELL problem
