@{b}Why doesn't the bugger work!!@{ub}
-----------------------------

If it doesn't work then you have done something to it and you had best
E-mail me! Address: Steve@unreal.demon.co.uk

If this registered version simply use the "Contact Author" program.

You will be presented with a choice of 2 programs.

1) Chat: Activates the Amitcp:bin/talk program direct to my address.
2) Mail: Activates my own mail program,
   (which can be used as annonymous mail if you fiddle around with it)
   and sends me a mail telling me of your problem which you specify in
   several boxes.

   Simply fill the selected boxes in like so:

   SUBJECT:  <The subject of your mail>

   Problem:  <What's wrong...you may waffle on as long as you like>

   Address:  <Your E-mail address, so that I can reply>

